---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import { SITE } from '../consts';
---
<BaseLayout
  title="About Penpixel Creative | Strategic AI Search Infrastructure"
  description="We build the infrastructure AI agents trust. Veteran SaaS strategists providing the diagnostic clarity to own your AI share of voice."
>
  <main>
    <section class="mx-auto max-w-6xl px-6 pt-20 pb-16 md:pt-28">
      <p class="font-mono text-sm uppercase tracking-[0.2em] text-impact">// about</p>
      <h1 class="mt-5 max-w-4xl text-5xl md:text-6xl">We Build the Infrastructure That AI Agents Trust.</h1>
      <p class="mt-6 max-w-2xl text-lg text-canvas/80">
        Penpixel Creative is a small team of veteran SaaS strategists. We started in SEO.
        We're not stuck there.
      </p>
    </section>

    <section class="border-t border-white/10">
      <div class="mx-auto max-w-6xl px-6 py-20">
        <h2 class="max-w-3xl text-3xl md:text-4xl">Visibility is a commodity. Authority is the asset.</h2>
        <div class="mt-8 grid gap-8 md:grid-cols-2">
          <p class="text-canvas/70">Anyone can be visible. Ranking for a keyword means little when an AI assistant is the one deciding what to recommend. The question that matters now is whether a model trusts your brand enough to put it in the answer.</p>
          <p class="text-canvas/70">That trust is built in the architecture — clean, server-rendered HTML, structured data, and a consistent entity across the entire web. It's engineering work, not marketing copy. That's the work we do.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="border-t border-white/10">
      <div class="mx-auto max-w-6xl px-6 py-20">
        <p class="font-mono text-sm uppercase tracking-[0.2em] text-canvas/50">// the approach</p>
        <h2 class="mt-5 max-w-3xl text-3xl md:text-4xl">We diagnose before we prescribe.</h2>
        <p class="mt-6 max-w-2xl text-canvas/70">
          No retainer-first pitch, no guesswork. Every engagement starts with a diagnosis:
          a precise read of where your brand is invisible or misread by AI systems, and a
          prioritized plan to fix it. You see the problem before you commit to the solution.
        </p>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="border-t border-white/10">
      <div class="mx-auto max-w-6xl px-6 py-20">
        <p class="font-mono text-sm uppercase tracking-[0.2em] text-canvas/50">// the team</p>
        <h2 class="mt-5 text-3xl md:text-4xl">The people behind the architecture.</h2>
        <div class="mt-10 grid gap-10 md:grid-cols-3">
          <article>
            <img src="/images/deven-bhagwandin.webp" alt="Deven Bhagwandin, Founder of Penpixel Creative" width="640" height="777" loading="lazy" class="w-full max-w-xs" />
            <p class="mt-5 font-mono text-xs uppercase tracking-[0.2em] text-impact">The Technical Strategist</p>
            <h3 class="mt-2 text-xl">{SITE.founder}</h3>
            <p class="font-display text-sm font-bold text-canvas/80">Strategic Vision. AI Authority.</p>
            <p class="mt-3 text-sm text-canvas/70">
              Deven leads the strategic direction at Penpixel Creative. His experience in executive
              consulting and digital communications helps business leaders navigate the critical
              shift from traditional SEO to AI-search readiness.
            </p>
            <p class="mt-3 text-sm text-canvas/70">
              An expert in Generative AI and Prompt Engineering, Deven decodes the logic of LLMs.
              He moves B2B leaders beyond keyword chasing and into &ldquo;Entity Hardening,&rdquo;
              ensuring your brand isn&rsquo;t just a result, but a recommendation.
            </p>
          </article>
          <article>
            <img src="/images/tony-moles.webp" alt="Tony Moles, Creative Director at Penpixel Creative" width="640" height="777" loading="lazy" class="w-full max-w-xs" />
            <p class="mt-5 font-mono text-xs uppercase tracking-[0.2em] text-success">The Creative Director</p>
            <h3 class="mt-2 text-xl">Tony Moles</h3>
            <p class="font-display text-sm font-bold text-canvas/80">Visual Authority. Strategic Execution.</p>
            <p class="mt-3 text-sm text-canvas/70">
              Tony brings veteran leadership to the creative process. With a background as a Creative
              Director in high-paced B2B agency environments, Tony doesn&rsquo;t just design assets;
              he engineers brand transformations.
            </p>
            <p class="mt-3 text-sm text-canvas/70">
              AI assesses &ldquo;Visual Trust.&rdquo; Tony engineers brand identities that signal
              enterprise-grade authority. He ensures your visual footprint is a consistent trust
              signal that reinforces your entity confidence score across every platform.
            </p>
          </article>
          <article>
            <img src="/images/patrick-mcdonough.webp" alt="Patrick McDonough, The Growth Architect at Penpixel Creative" width="400" height="400" loading="lazy" class="w-full max-w-xs" />
            <p class="mt-5 font-mono text-xs uppercase tracking-[0.2em] text-ai">The Growth Architect</p>
            <h3 class="mt-2 text-xl">Patrick McDonough</h3>
            <p class="font-display text-sm font-bold text-canvas/80">Entrepreneurial DNA. Commercial Velocity.</p>
            <p class="mt-3 text-sm text-canvas/70">
              Patrick applies a founder&rsquo;s mindset to marketing execution. With a track record
              that includes founding multiple multi-million dollar companies and creating marketing
              programs for hundreds of successful organizations, Patrick moves beyond theory to
              focus entirely on ROI.
            </p>
            <p class="mt-3 text-sm text-canvas/70">
              With a founder&rsquo;s focus on ROI, Patrick brings VC-level discipline to marketing
              operations. He ensures your AI-readiness infrastructure is built for one purpose:
              measurable, scalable revenue growth.
            </p>
          </article>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="border-t border-white/10">
      <div class="mx-auto max-w-6xl px-6 py-24">
        <h2 class="max-w-3xl text-4xl md:text-5xl">See where you stand.</h2>
        <a href="/contact" class="mt-8 inline-block bg-impact px-8 py-4 font-display text-lg font-bold text-canvas transition-opacity hover:opacity-90">Get the Diagnosis</a>
      </div>
    </section>
  </main>
</BaseLayout>
